name: 2023 15th International Conference on Bioinformatics and Biomedical Technology
content: Publication and Indexing: Papers accepted by ICBBT 2023 will be published in ACM International Conference Proceedings (ISBN: 979-8-4007-0038-5), which will be archived by ACM Digital Library, indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus, and submitted to be reviewed by CPCI (ISI Web of Science). Special Issue-SCI &Scopus Journal (IF: 2.940; Cite Score: 4.3): Selected papers with at least 50% extention will be recommended for reviewing of publication in the Symmetry (ISSN: 2073-8994) as a special issue, which will be indexed by Scopus, SCIE (Web of Science), Inspec, and many other databases.
